Corona is spreading more and more, every day we hear new cases have shown up.
Today I found myself looking for the stats, wasn't hard to find, but that made me think why won't I create a bot that posts the stats of corona in morocco every day.
That's exactly what I present to you today, a bot that fetches the data by itself, and posts the stats on the page.
